verbose_text: In mouse, CCs a significantly lower expression of Esr1 was seen in oocytes at 12 and 24 h post-hCG compared to 9 h whereas no significant difference was detected in CCs associated with oocytes at 15 and 21 h. Foxo1, Foxo3 and Foxo4 expression modulation in mouse CCs was variable at the different maturation times as reported in Fig. XREF_FIG.
